Class ExtendedUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jacktheclipper.frontend.model.MinimalUser

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.security.Principal

    public class ExtendedUser
extends User
    An extension to User. Normally for this application it is irrelevant to which OrganizationalUnit a user belongs to. The only OrganizationalUnit the User cares about is his principal unit. Since a user can belong to multiple subunits of his principal unit this class is needed to represent this additional information so that an UserRole.StaffChief can manage it.
